<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN339">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>viyaṉpulam paṭarnta pallā neṭuvēṟu</l>
<l>maṭalai māṇiḻa lacaiviṭak kōvalar</l>
<l>vītatai mullaip pūppaṟik kuntu</l>
<l>kuṟuṅkō leṟinta neṭuñcevik kuṟumuya</l>
<l>ṉeṭunīrp parappiṉ vāḷaiyo ṭukaḷuntu</l>
<l>toṭalai yalkuṟ ṟoṭittōṇ makaḷir</l>
<l>kaṭalāṭik kayampāyntu</l>
<l>kaḻineytaṟ pūkkuṟūuntu</l>
<l>paintaḻai tuyalvaruñ ceṟuviṟ ṟa<gap quantity="8" reason="lost" unit="character"/></l>
<l><gap quantity="36" reason="lost" unit="character"/>latti</l>
<l>vaḷara vēṇṭu mavaḷē yeṉṟu</l>
<l>mārama ruḻappatu mamariya ḷāki</l>
<l>muṟañcevi yāṉai vēntar</l>
<l>maṟaṅkeḻu neñcaṅ koṇṭoḷit tōḷē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Where, while the large bull of many cows that set out for the wide fields</l>
<l>chew the cud in the glorious shade of the Maṭalai tree, the cowherds</l>
<l>pull out the flowers of the jasmine in dense bloom,</l>
<l>while the little hare with long ears that is hit with a short stick</l>
<l>is leaping along with the Vāḷai fish in the expanse of long water,</l>
<l>while women with bangled arms [and] wreath[-covered] hips</l>
<l>bathe in the sea, jump into tanks</l>
<l>[and] pluck the flowers of the waterlily in the backwaters,</l>
<l>in the fields where [their] fresh leaf skirt come into swinging…………..</l>
<l>……………</l>
<l>although ? says “she must [still] grow”,</l>
<l>being a girl for battle, something that endures difficult fights,</l>
<l>she had taken [and] hidden the bold hearts</l>
<l>of kings on elephant with winnow ears.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
